<div id="change-b0802b378c49fa8e3c59530b2d64182bbc6dc13d" class="metadata">
<span class="desc"><br />Changed pages:</span>
<span class="pagelinks">


<a href="http://source.liw-fi.branchable.com/?p=source.git;a=blobdiff;f=ideas/bug-names.mdwn;h=2b4837f978834e73200ebb37a7d965908262ab14;hp=0000000000000000000000000000000000000000;hb=b0802b378c49fa8e3c59530b2d64182bbc6dc13d;hpb=90afa27f70bf04fd2bb8f6df242f26c3e868a635" title="diff" rel="nofollow"><img src="../wikiicons/diff.png" alt="diff" /></a><a href="/ikiwiki.cgi?page=ideas%2Fbug-names&amp;do=goto" rel="nofollow">ideas/bug-names</a>


